profile:
At Bostech Mechanical we specialize in geothermal heating & cooling systems for residential and commercial applications. We also do in-floor & hydronic heating, air purification, pool heat pumps, heat recovery ventilators & furnaces, air conditioners, boiler systems, & ductwork.

Please Call, email or visit us for a free estimate on any of our HVAC products or services.

As an accredited CGC company and leading geothermal dealer we guarantee you expert design, installation and service. Bostech assures you that through the installation of the best technology available and meeting the CGC designing and installation standards of the geothermal industry, your home will have a cost-effective geothermal system that meets your needs and keeps you in comfort all year round.
